"Template" refers to the Netflix Birthday personalised website template, including all source code, design systems, component architecture, animation logic, documentation, and structural files contained in this repository.

"You" or "Licensee" refers to the individual who has obtained this Template for personal use.

"Personalised Version" refers to a deployment of this Template where You have replaced placeholder content (names, dates, photos, messages, music) with Your own personal content.

